// segment_arena_backing_modeled_allocation_ledger_release_recycle_execution_support_requirement_matrix_diagnostic_box.hako -- MIMAP-329A
// Responsibility:
// - observe MIMAP-328A support requirement matrix facts and publish scalar/model
//   diagnostics
// - keep diagnostics observer-only before any real release/recycle execution
//   opens
// Non-responsibility:
// - recording requirement matrix rows, satisfying requirements, executing real
//   release/recycle, lifecycle generation, pointer residence, segment-map
//   mutation, atomic bitmap execution, OSVM calls, scheduling, providers, or
//   backend shortcuts

